- "outshines all others on the track" means the driver is ranked first in terms of average speed on the track.

sql:
SELECT race_id, COUNT(caution_id) AS number_of_cautions
FROM cautions
GROUP BY race_id;

SELECT state, speed_avg
FROM races
WHERE speed_avg = (SELECT MAX(speed_avg) FROM races);

